video.title: Degrassi: Next Class
video.synopsis: Degrassi's next generation of high-tech newbies and returning students navigates real-world high school drama. If you're a teen, this is your life.

episodes.synopsis: A school election brings up past heartbreak between Tristan and Miles. Maya is forced to choose between her music and Zig. Shay feels inadequate.
episodes.title: #BootyCall

episodes.synopsis: Miles sees something he wishes he hadn't. Frankie feels like her friends don't understand her anymore. Grace's standoffish behavior worries Zoë.
episodes.title: #NoFilter

episodes.synopsis: Seeing that his mom is quick to forgive, Miles feels betrayed. Tiny coaches Zig to be more assertive. Hunter submits a request to the student council.
episodes.title: #YesMeansYes

episodes.synopsis: Sexist digs get Maya riled up at her band's first gig. Tristan tries to move on. Shay allows fear to get in the way of accepting an invitation.
episodes.title: #NotOkay

episodes.synopsis: Maya and her pals debate the definition of "feminist." Miles finds healthy and unhealthy ways to cope with anxiety. Lola learns to love herself.
episodes.title: #ButThatsNoneOfMyBusiness

episodes.synopsis: Feeling unaccepted by her mom, Zoë searches for her dad. The gamer club lands in hot water over misogyny. Frankie wonders if she's self-absorbed.
episodes.title: #NotAllMen

episodes.synopsis: Zig feels insecure when Maya and Jonah go to New York to visit a producer. Miles spirals out of control. Zoë and Grace try being more than friends.
episodes.title: #ThisCouldBeUsButYouPlayin

episodes.synopsis: Publicly embarrassed, Tristan gets sympathy from an unlikely source. Hateful online attention spooks Maya. Frankie's heart leads her to a surprise.
episodes.title: #TeamFollowBack

episodes.synopsis: Frankie is unsure how to proceed with her current love interest. Miles finds it difficult to avoid Esme. The online troll threatening Maya is found.
episodes.title: #SinceWeBeinHonest

episodes.synopsis: Miles breaks some news to Tristan. Maya confronts Zoë. Frankie chooses between her two suitors. Hunter goes off the deep end.
episodes.title: #SorryNotSorry

episodes.synopsis: Thoughts of Zig distract Maya as she tries to land a co-op with a music producer. Miles makes a change of plans after Hunter pulls a dangerous stunt.
episodes.title: #SquadGoals

episodes.synopsis: A forced stay at a psychiatric facility gives Hunter time to reflect. Shay questions whether Frankie should be excused for pulling the banner prank.
episodes.title: #TurntUp

episodes.synopsis: Yael compromises her values to boost her app's popularity. Frankie's feeble attempts at apologizing to Northern Tech change Shay's opinion of her.
episodes.title: #CheckYourPrivilege

episodes.synopsis: Tiny learns Lola has been using a dating app. Grace worries she looks unapproachable. Desperate to be liked, Zoë pretends to be something she's not.
episodes.title: #BuyMePizza

episodes.synopsis: When Lola stages a protest of Tiny's suspension, Tristan tries to prevent it from affecting the alumni gala. Frankie is haunted by her bad reputation.
episodes.title: #ThrowbackThursday

episodes.synopsis: Shay is offered Olympic-level training, but with a condition. Winston comes to Zoë's defense when she's accused of being racially insensitive.
episodes.title: #ToMyFutureSelf

episodes.synopsis: To avoid her classmates, Frankie runs away with Jonah. A health crisis leads Tiny and Lola to a realization about their feelings for each other.
episodes.title: #ThatAwkwardMomentWhen

episodes.synopsis: A game of truth or dare makes Tristan feel insecure in his relationship with Miles. Zig's smooth moves catch the eye of a job recruiter.
episodes.title: #RiseAndGrind

episodes.synopsis: After Grace acts on a romantic impulse, her secret is revealed. Shay wonders if she should forgive Frankie. Yael goes on the date she owes to Baaz.
episodes.title: #TheseAreMyConfessions

episodes.synopsis: Shay asks Lola for permission to date Tiny. Zoë can no longer keep up her charade with Winston. Surprise visitors ruin Hunter and Yael's first date.
episodes.title: #OMFG

episodes.synopsis: One student is unable to return for the start of the new school year. Zoë takes a brave step. A jealous Lola lashes out.
episodes.title: #BreakTheInternet

episodes.synopsis: The gamer club's plan to attract more female viewers to their YouTube channel backfires. Esme reveals to Zig a dark burden she's carrying.
episodes.title: #IWokeUpLikeThis

episodes.synopsis: Shay suffers a feminine mishap. Miles finds it hard to continue visiting Tristan. Goldi struggles with being a Muslim in a largely non-Muslim culture.
episodes.title: #WorstGiftEver

episodes.synopsis: Frankie gets suspicious when Jonah refuses to show her a text message from Grace. Maya meets a student who shares her dark interests.
episodes.title: #PicsOrItDidntHappen

episodes.synopsis: Hunter, Vijay and Baaz decide to see how they measure up to one another. A girls' night turns into a coed party and leads to an unexpected hookup.
episodes.title: #HugeIfTrue

episodes.synopsis: Zoë and Winston vie for a date with Rasha. A development at the hospital stresses out Miles. An insecure Frankie finds herself stalking Jonah.
episodes.title: #ThatFeelingWhen

episodes.synopsis: Grace faces a difficult decision about her health. Rasha's first date goes awry. Hunter suffers an embarrassment. Zoë is caught in an intimate moment.
episodes.title: #Unsubscribe

episodes.synopsis: Lola takes a nerve-wracking test. Tristan makes progress. Maya sinks further into her depression. Miles worries that the play may be too revealing.
episodes.title: #IRegretNothing

episodes.synopsis: Maya comes up with a plan to stop her hurtful behavior. Zoë makes a bold statement at her mom's wedding. Frankie is caught violating others' privacy.
episodes.title: #Woke

episodes.synopsis: Tristan goes to see the school play. Rasha comes out to Goldi. An unlikely student finds Maya in the wake of her misguided plan.
episodes.title: #ImSleep

episodes.synopsis: Jonah hides a secret from Frankie. Yael grapples with body issues. Maya's return to school draws Zig's attention — and Esme's jealousy.
episodes.title: #BackToReality

episodes.synopsis: Frankie's attempt at posting happier photos on her social media feed backfires. Shay grows desperate for a competitive edge in her athletic training.
episodes.title: #GetMoney

episodes.synopsis: A shocking photo hurts Goldi and Winston's friendship. Miles is thrilled by an invitation to a writing program, until he learns it's a diversity spot.
episodes.title: #ILookLikeA

episodes.synopsis: Grace decides to write up a bucket list. Maya rediscovers the fun of music. A terrorist attack overseas puts Goldi in a scary situation close to home.
episodes.title: #RollUpToTheClubLike

episodes.synopsis: Saad is misunderstood when he questions a show of support for the Brussels terrorist attack victims. A rumor circulates about Frankie, Esme and Zig.
episodes.title: #Preach

episodes.synopsis: Esme and Frankie distract Zig after he gets bad news. A talent show performance earns Maya an offer. Yael seeks Lola's help with an image makeover.
episodes.title: #FactsOnly

episodes.synopsis: During a camping trip, Maya suffers from songwriter's block, Frankie learns the real reason Esme befriended her, and Tiny and Shay get closer.
episodes.title: #Fire

episodes.synopsis: Saad confides in Lola, who helps him out of a troubling situation. Shay awaits a "promposal" from Tiny. Tristan pushes himself too hard in rehab.
episodes.title: #GetYouAManWhoCanDoBoth

episodes.synopsis: A scare delays the prom and brings the police. Esme shows up at the dance and makes a scene. Miles talks with his father about his near-future plans.
episodes.title: #Obsessed

episodes.synopsis: Zoë invites her estranged mother to her graduation. Esme makes a last-ditch effort to win back Zig. The truth about the bomb threat comes out.
episodes.title: #KThxBye
